    <item>
      <title>Oak Hill 为 Worldpac 提供 7.75 亿美元私人贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/oak-hill-provides-775-million-private-loan-for-worldpac</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，Oak Hill Advisors 已提供了 7.75 亿美元的私人信贷贷款，帮助凯雷集团 (Carlyle Group Inc.) 融资收购汽车零部件分销商 Worldpac。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/oak-hill-provides-775-million-private-loan-for-worldpac</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 14:43:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>银行私人信贷风险受到欧元区监管机构的新一轮审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/banks-private-credit-exposures-under-fresh-scrutiny-from-eurozone-regulators</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士向彭博新闻社表示，欧洲央行正在敦促主要银行提供与私人信贷公司交易的更多细节，这是全球为保护传统金融业免受潜在影子银行危机影响而采取的最新举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/banks-private-credit-exposures-under-fresh-scrutiny-from-eurozone-regulators</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 14:42:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多放宽抵押贷款规定以吸引年轻选民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/trudeau-loosens-mortgage-rules-in-bid-to-help-younger-voters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[陷入困境的总理贾斯汀·特鲁多 (Justin Trudeau) 试图重新赢得年轻加拿大人的认可，他领导的政府将向所有首次购房者和新建住宅的购房者提供 30 年期抵押贷款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/trudeau-loosens-mortgage-rules-in-bid-to-help-younger-voters</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 14:40:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>奥孔乔-伊韦阿拉同意竞选世贸组织总干事第二任期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/wto-says-okonjo-iweala-to-seek-second-term-as-director-general</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世界贸易组织总干事恩戈齐·奥孔乔·伊韦阿拉正在寻求连任，因为这个国际贸易规则制定机构正面临来自部分创始成员国日益抬头的保护主义。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/wto-says-okonjo-iweala-to-seek-second-term-as-director-general</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 14:16:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德对债券发出警告，称对美联储利率的押注过度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/blackrock-warns-on-bonds-saying-fed-rate-cut-bets-are-overdone</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德公司策略师将对短期美国国债的持仓评级从增持转为减持，称市场押注的美联储降息幅度不太可能实现。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/blackrock-warns-on-bonds-saying-fed-rate-cut-bets-are-overdone</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
