      <title>阿拉比卡咖啡期货因供应担忧创下 2011 年以来新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/arabica-coffee-soars-to-most-since-2011-as-supply-woes-escalate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于持续的供应中断导致优质阿拉比卡咖啡豆的成本升至 13 年来的最高水平，一杯咖啡的价格将进一步上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/arabica-coffee-soars-to-most-since-2011-as-supply-woes-escalate</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 08:35:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
